    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative execution of the S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been meticulously calibrated for peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension refreshed with OEM-spec bushings to maintain its legendary kinematics. Power is managed via a tactile six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. The exterior displays factory-depth paint with zero orange peel or panel gap irregularities, while the interior's Nappa leather bolsters remain firm and unblemished. Preventative rod bearing replacement has been performed to ensure long-term mechanical integrity, making this a true collector-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
