    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating applied to protect against the elements\u2014not a single stone chip or swirl mark to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships and brand-new performance tires. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
